        {
            "jpName": "マンハッタンカフェ",
            "enName": "Manhattan Cafe",
            "jpText": "何かから解き放たれたように、とても速くて。\r\n差は……見たこともないほど広がって……。",
            "enText": "It was as if I had been freed from\nsomething, and very fast. The difference\n… widened and… widened like\nnothing I had ever seen before.",
